# Merchant WebApp Configuration

## xPay Backend API Configuration
# URL of the xPay Backend service for checkout session creation
VITE_XPAY_BACKEND_URL=http://localhost:3001

## Application Port
# Port where the development server runs
VITE_APP_PORT=5173

## Environment
# Set to 'production' during build for production deployments
# NODE_ENV is controlled by Vite/build tool automatically
# NODE_ENV=development
